{"build_type":"library","module_name":"resolve-reclaim-ring-base-for-size","package_name":"resolve-reclaim-ring-base-for-size","description":"Reclaim-ring size-class router: the slab holds 3 class sizes (slab[0..2]) and 3 rings (slab+24, stride 65560B = 24B control + 4096*16B slots). Returns the ring base for an exact-size class match, else 0 (uncommon sizes bypass the ring). Exact match, so a dequeued chunk always satisfies the request with no too-small case.","function_definitions":{"resolve-reclaim-ring-base-for-size":{"return_type":"i64","parameter_definitions":[{"parameter_name":"slab","parameter_type":"i64"},{"parameter_name":"size","parameter_type":"i64"}],"execution_instructions":[{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"zero","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":0},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"one","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":1},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"two","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":2},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"s24","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":24},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"stride","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":65560},{"instruction_type":"array_read","dest":"cs0","base":"slab","index":"zero","scale":8},{"instruction_type":"array_read","dest":"cs1","base":"slab","index":"one","scale":8},{"instruction_type":"array_read","dest":"cs2","base":"slab","index":"two","scale":8},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"rb","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":0},{"instruction_type":"alu_operation","operator":"+","target":"rb","lhs":{"value":"slab"},"rhs":{"value":"s24"}},{"instruction_type":"conditional_branch","condition_type":"numeric_compare","operator":"==","